author: Nerd of the Rings
description:
Check out Woodsted Studios on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/woodstedstudios/

Today, we unbox a kingly gift from our friend at Woodsted Studios!  One of the most memorable pieces of concept art from The Hobbit films is Thorin Oakenshield's royal armor - one version with a raven helm.  Woodsted Studios has recreated this EPIC helm in one of the most jaw-dropping pieces I've ever unboxed!

#thehobbit #helmet #unboxing
title: The Raven Helm of Thorin Oakenshield
